2 Visualisation

2.1 Non racinÃ©

Impossible de distinguer les labels quand un noeud nâest pas rÃ©solu.

Tout de mÃªme, on repÃ¨re un noeud central avec un bootstrap Ã  100 qui fera office de pseudo racine.

Le noeud 223 fera lâaffaire.

tree.day <- ggtree(tree, layout="daylight") %<+% 
  strains_scer_all[c("strain_name","label_phylo")]

tree.day + 
  geom_tiplab(aes(angle = angle), color='black', size = 2) +
  geom_tippoint(aes(color = label_phylo), size=2) +
  geom_text(aes(label=node), hjust=-.3, size = 2) +
  geom_nodelab(color = "darkblue", size = 2) +
  theme(legend.position = "bottom") +
  labs(color = "")

tree.rt <- root(tree, node = 223)
tree.rt.fan <- ggtree(tree.rt, layout="fan")
tree.rt.fan$data$label_phylo <- strains_scer_all$label_phylo[match(tree.rt.fan$data$label,
                                                                   strains_scer_all$strain_name)]
tree.rt.fan$data$boot <- ifelse(as.numeric(tree.rt.fan$data$label) > 98,
                                TRUE, FALSE)

tree.rt.fan <- tree.rt.fan + 
  geom_tiplab(aes(angle = angle), color='black', size = 2, offset = 0.001) +
  geom_nodepoint(aes(alpha = boot), size = 1, show.legend = F) +
  geom_tippoint(aes(color = label_phylo), size=1.5) +
  scale_color_manual(values = c("#F98400","#00A08A","#FF0000","purple")) +
  theme(legend.position = "bottom") +
  labs(color = "")

tree.rt.fan

myggsave(cowplot::get_legend(tree.rt.fan),
